<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Axion Dashboard</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/img/axion-logo.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css?v=20260329-7">
</head>
<body>
  <main class="container layout">
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="logo-wrap">
        <img class="logo" style="width:24px;height:24px;max-width:24px;max-height:24px;min-width:24px;min-height:24px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" src="/img/axion-logo.png" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='/img/axion-logo.svg';" alt="Axion">
        <div>
          <div class="brand-title">AXION</div>
          <div class="brand-sub">Control Center</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="theme-picker">
        <button class="theme-btn" data-theme="default">Default</button>
        <button class="theme-btn" data-theme="neon">Neon</button>
        <button class="theme-btn" data-theme="sunset">Sunset</button>
        <button class="theme-btn" data-theme="emerald">Emerald</button>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <section class="main">
      <section class="hero">
        <h1>Axion Dashboard</h1>
        <p>A clean control panel for moderation, safety, and community management across all your servers.</p>
        <div class="actions">
          <% if (user) { %>
            <a class="btn" href="/dashboard">Open Dashboard</a>
            <a class="btn secondary" href="/logout">Logout</a>
          <% } else { %>
            <a class="btn" href="/login">Login with Discord</a>
          <% } %>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="<%= inviteUrl %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Invite Axion</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <h2>About <%= bot?.name || 'Axion' %></h2>
        <p class="muted">Axion is built for real server workflows: fast moderation actions, configurable safety systems, and tools that help staff stay organized.</p>
        <div class="compact-stats">
          <div class="compact-stat"><span>Servers</span><strong><%= bot?.guildCount || 0 %></strong></div>
          <div class="compact-stat"><span>Slash Commands</span><strong><%= bot?.commandCount || 0 %></strong></div>
          <div class="compact-stat"><span>Bot Tag</span><strong><%= bot?.tag || 'Axion' %></strong></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="grid cols-2">
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Core moderation</h3>
          <p class="muted">Warn, timeout, kick, ban, unban, clear, lock/unlock, and slowmode with proper role-gated permissions and case history tracking.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Server safety</h3>
          <p class="muted">Automod includes anti-spam, anti-invite, mention filtering, and customizable limits to reduce raids and abuse.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Community systems</h3>
          <p class="muted">Tickets, reaction roles, starboard, suggestions, verification, tags, AFK, notes, and welcome flows are all available per guild.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Logs and insights</h3>
          <p class="muted">Track message edits/deletes and moderation activity, then tune your setup from the dashboard without touching config files.</p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <h3>Quick start</h3>
        <ol class="quick-list">
          <li>Invite Axion to your server.</li>
          <li>Open the dashboard and select your server.</li>
          <li>Set moderator/admin roles in the Roles tab.</li>
          <li>Enable modules like automod, welcomer, and logging.</li>
        </ol>
      </section>
    </section>
  </main>
  <script src="/js/theme.js?v=20260329-7"></script>
</body>
</html>
